  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2709700/extras/26722ace7024c6c81681ac173290e655.poster.avif?t=1725042935\" width=616 height=232 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2709700/extras/26722ace7024c6c81681ac173290e655.webm?t=1725042935\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2709700/extras/26722ace7024c6c81681ac173290e655.mp4?t=1725042935\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Flob and the Shattered Dimension is a platformer game where you can test your skills while traversing various stages filled with challenging obstacles. Get ready to face spitting fishes, wasps, evil rocks, and... predators from other dimensions?!<br>Explore the world and search for a way to rescue your creator, Dr. Franz!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2709700/extras/e147ee0294c5c6c2221c4b25992b456d.poster.avif?t=1725042935\" width=800 height=290 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2709700/extras/e147ee0294c5c6c2221c4b25992b456d.webm?t=1725042935\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2709700/extras/e147ee0294c5c6c2221c4b25992b456d.mp4?t=1725042935\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Features:<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 50+ Rooms<br></li><li> 3 Worlds<br></li><li> 15+ Collectibles<br></li><li> 7 Achievements<br></li><li> 6 Original soundtracks<br></li><li> The ability to fly in another dimension!</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2709700/extras/26722ace7024c6c81681ac173290e655.poster.avif?t=1725042935\" width=616 height=232 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2709700/extras/26722ace7024c6c81681ac173290e655.webm?t=1725042935\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2709700/extras/26722ace7024c6c81681ac173290e655.mp4?t=1725042935\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Flob and the Shattered Dimension is a platformer game where you can test your skills while traversing various stages filled with challenging obstacles. Get ready to face spitting fishes, wasps, evil rocks, and... predators from other dimensions?!<br>Explore the world and search for a way to rescue your creator, Dr. Franz!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2709700/extras/e147ee0294c5c6c2221c4b25992b456d.poster.avif?t=1725042935\" width=800 height=290 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2709700/extras/e147ee0294c5c6c2221c4b25992b456d.webm?t=1725042935\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2709700/extras/e147ee0294c5c6c2221c4b25992b456d.mp4?t=1725042935\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Features:<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 50+ Rooms<br></li><li> 3 Worlds<br></li><li> 15+ Collectibles<br></li><li> 7 Achievements<br></li><li> 6 Original soundtracks<br></li><li> The ability to fly in another dimension!</li></ul>",
